t%20all%20issues%20can%20be%20resolved%20at%20once%2C%20Seoul%20is%20confident%20that%20continuous%20efforts%20and%20various%20innovative%20attempts%20will%20eventually%20lead%20to%20achieving%20its%20goals.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeoul%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20its%20utmost%20to%20create%20a%20city%20where%20all%20citizens%20can%20live%20happily%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20country's%20Ministry%20of%20Gender%20Equality%20and%20Family%20said%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mogef.go.kr%2Fnw%2Frpd%2Fnw_rpd_s001d.do%3Fmid%3Dnews405%26bbtSn%3D709207%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20socially%20isolated%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20%24500%20a%20month%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20mingle%20with%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228922bc6c-408d-4ea5-8ce9-57ebff818123%5C%22%3EPrevention%20is%20better%20than%20cure%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20tackling%20loneliness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPsychologists%20and%20sociologists%20that%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20while%20October's%20initiative%20is%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20silver%20bullet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20helpful%20for%20those%20who%20feel%20they're%20isolated%20and%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20get%20out%20of%20their%20loneliness.%20But%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20want%20outside%20help%2C%20then%20these%20policies%20are%20probably%20irrelevant%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Joonmo%20Son%2C%20a%20sociology%20professor%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20issue%20we%20need%20to%20think%20of%20is%20that%20the%20policy%20itself%20does%20not%20prevent%20loneliness.%20Rather%2C%20it's%20to%20prevent%20the%20lonely%20deaths%20of%20those%20who%20are%20isolated%2C%26quot%3B%20Son%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEva%20Chen%2C%20a%20psychology%20professor%20at%20Taiwan's%20National%20Tsing%20Hua%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20South%20Korea%20should%20address%20the%20country's%20competitive%20culture%2C%20which%20starts%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20nearly%2080%25%20of%20children%20participated%20in%20private%20education%20programs%20like%20%26quot%3Bhagwons%26quot%3B%20or%20cram%20schools%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkostat.go.kr%2Fboard.es%3Fmid%3Da20111020000%26bid%3D11758%26act%3Dview%26list_no%3D430448%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20South%20Korea's%20National%20Statistics%20Office.%20Families%20also%20splashed%20out%20%2419.4%20billion%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-koreas-education-fever-needs-cooling-2013-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20span%20all%20manner%20of%20supplementary%20drilling%20on%20schoolwork%2C%20from%20after-school%20%26quot%3Bhagwon%26quot%3B%20sessions%20to%20tutoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20incredibly%20competitive%20society%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20these%20issues%20start%20to%20appear%20when%20children%20start%20their%20formal%20schooling.%20You%20will%20notice%20that%20suicide%20rates%20among%20Korean%20students%20are%20fairly%20high%20when%20compared%20to%20neighboring%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Chen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20South%20Korea%20recorded%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F789337%2Fsouth-korea-suicide-death-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuicide%20rate%20of%2027.3%20out%20of%20100%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20among%20OECD%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavigating%20such%20a%20competitive%20environment%2C%20Chen%20said%2C%20can%20result%20in%20people%20becoming%20more%20withdrawn%20and%20isolated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sort%20of%20breaks%20down%20that%20willingness%20to%20be%20helpful.%20In%20young%20children%2C%20the%20natural%20tendency%20is%20toward%20empathy%20and%20valuing%20moral%20goodness%20over%20more%20superficial%20factors%20like%20your%20salary%20and%20your%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKee%20Hong%20Choi%2C%20a%20psychology%20professor%20at%20Korea%20University%2C%20said%20that%20his%20country's%20education%20system%20needs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bchanged%20dramatically%26quot%3B%20to%20become%20less%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20become%20individualistic%20because%20they%20are%20emotionally%20hardened%20from%20social%20pressure%20and%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20Choi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20get%20traumatized%20by%20these%20kinds%20of%20social%20comparisons%20in%20an%20education%20system%20and%20start%20to%20develop%20depressive%2C%20or%20social%20anxiety%20symptoms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c41b5b63-5efc-4e27-a302-e5f7a29c771b%5C%22%3EStakes%20are%20high%20for%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20loneliness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20ongoing%20struggle%20with%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%20poses%20both%20social%20and%20economic%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESohyun%20Kim%2C%20a%20psychology%20professor%20at%20Korea%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20problem%20of%20loneliness%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20urgent%20social%20and%20economic%20problems%26quot%3B%20the%20country%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20these%20individuals%20are%20also%20financially%20struggling%2C%20which%20is%20not%20surprising%20as%20all%20of%20these%20issues%20can%20affect%20various%20areas%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20including%20our%20productivity%2C%20and%20also%20those%20who%20are%20financially%20more%20limited%20have%20been%20found%20to%20be%20at%20higher%20risk%20of%20isolation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKorea%20University's%20Choi%20said%20social%20isolation%20among%20youths%2