s%20more%20than%20base%20pay%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKetaki%20Vaidya%20had%20worked%20in%20Oracle's%20office%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20India%20for%20about%20five%20years%20when%20she%20wanted%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20be%20part%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20innovations.%20She%20negotiated%20a%20move%20to%20California%20in%202022%20and%20has%20since%20transferred%20to%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaidya%20shared%20how%2C%20over%20seven%20years%20with%20Oracle%2C%20she%20navigated%20two%20promotions%2C%20a%20career%20change%2C%20and%20the%20international%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fd29ec1-13ce-4d32-b17d-ff3b8f021893%5C%22%3EAssociate%20software%20engineer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20began%20her%20post-college%20career%20as%20an%20associate%20software%20engineer%20at%20Oracle's%20office%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20Vaidya%20did%20was%20gauge%20what%20her%20entire%20team%20wanted%20from%20her%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20only%20on%20her%20supervisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManagers%20always%20take%20360-degree%20feedback%2C%20and%20they%20go%20around%20the%20entire%20team%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20entire%20team%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20your%20work%20is%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20keep%20your%20team%20happy%2C%20you%20automatically%20keep%20your%20supervisor%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20scheduled%20regular%20check-ins%20with%20her%20manager%20to%20get%20feedback%20and%20she%20highlighted%20her%20aspirations%2C%20like%20working%20with%20particular%20software%2C%20so%20that%20her%20manager%20could%20tap%20her%20when%20the%20opportunity%20came%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20made%20about%20900%2C000%20Indian%20rupees%2C%20or%20%2410%2C700%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9dd9cff-3e43-4d32-977a-75169a4d62a7%5C%22%3ESoftware%20engineer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVaidya%20was%20promoted%20to%20software%20engineer%20after%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20followed%20female%20role%20models%20who%20reminded%20her%20to%20credit%20herself%2C%20not%20just%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20vocal%20meant%20always%20discussing%20her%20next%20promotion%20and%20growth%20opportunity%20with%20managers.%20She%20made%20sure%20to%20document%20and%20communicate%20her%20successes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20knew%20that%20I%20was%20very%20invested%20in%20my%20career%2C%20and%20then%20my%20managers%20would%20really%20help%20me%20all%20around%20the%20year%20to%20get%20better%20projects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20role%2C%20Vaidya%20was%20paid%201.2%20million%20rupees%2C%20or%20%2414%2C200%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6607906-b1a9-44bd-b26d-a2a80b8ac901%5C%22%3ESenior%20software%20engineer%20and%20team%20lead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20years%20at%20the%20company%2C%20Vaidya%20was%20promoted%20to%20senior%20engineer%2C%20where%20she%20led%20a%20team%20of%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20her%20projects%2C%20Vaidya%20said%20she%20found%20ways%20to%20demonstrate%20her%20work%20to%20leadership%2C%20like%20sharing%20what%20she%20learned%20on%20the%20team's%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20carefully%20filled%20out%20her%20annual%20appraisal%20documents%2C%20drafting%20them%20several%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20take%20that%20very%20seriously%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20that%20goes%20into%20the%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20going%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20every%20time%20you%20move%20up%20the%20ladder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20role%2C%20Vaidya%20was%20paid%202%20million%20Indian%20rupees%2C%20or%20about%20%2424%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22feaee59b-071a-4db0-be63-eb91660c9f96%5C%22%3EShifting%20roles%20and%20US%20transfer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20progressed%2C%20Vaidya%20felt%20pulled%20to%20product%20management.%20She%20used%20her%20free%20time%20during%20the%20pandemic%20to%20chart%20what%20a%20job%20with%20more%20business%20strategy%20could%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20set%20up%2015-minute%20sessions%20with%20about%20200%20people%20on%20LinkedIn%20to%20understand%20what%20this%20field%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20talked%20to%20people%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realized%20it%20was%20something%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20think%20she%20had%20all%20the%20necessary%20skills%2C%20so%20she%20applied%20for%20master's%20courses%20specializing%20in%20product%20management%20in%20the%20US%2C%20so%20that%20she%20could%20better%20understand%20global%20work%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20resign%2C%20Oracle%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20want%20to%20let%20me%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Her%20job%20was%20critical%20to%20releasing%20a%20product%2C%20so%20the%20company%20offered%20her%20a%20product%20management%20role%20in%20the%20US%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20negotiated%20a%20new%20salary%20with%20an%20eye%20toward%20the%20much%20higher%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20Oracle%20was%20taking%20on%20significant%20costs%2C%20including%20for%20her%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20let%20the%20excitement%20show%20in%20the%20conversations%20that%20you're%20having%20with%20your%20hiring%20managers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20gather%20salary%20data%2C%20Vaidya%20looked%20at%20Glassdoor%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20talked%20to%20people%20who%20had%20made%20the%20move%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20being%20given%20this%20offer%20for%20the%20credibility%20that%20I%20had%20built%20in%20the%20organization.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20negotiating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20much%20more%20confident%20in%20asking%20for%20the%20things%20that%20I%20deserve%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20very%20smooth%20transition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20negotiating%20her%20base%20salary%20up%20to%20%2480%2C000%2C%20she%20discussed%20other%20compensation%20components%2C%20including%20her%20next%20review's%20timing%2C%20sign-on%20bonuses%2C%20relocation%20costs%2C%20paid%20leave%2C%20and%20remote%20work.%20She%20negotiated%20a%20sign-on%20bonus%20of%20%2415%2C000%20and%20relocation%20allowance%20of%20%2415%2C000%2C%20which%20weren't%20part%20of%20the%20initial%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20under%20the%20sun%20is%20negotiable%20and%20you%20just%20have%20to%20start%20with%20that%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20move%20took%20her%20to%20Redwood%20City%2C%20California%2C%20where%20she%20is%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20product%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20since%20moved%20to%20Seattle%20and%20plans%20to%20explore%20working%20in%20other%20US%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaidya%20said%20that%20she%20has%20picked%20up%20two%20things%20from%20the%20work%20culture%20in%20the%20US%3A%20She%20has%20been%20inspired%20to%20work%20on%20projects%20beyond%20her%20job%2C%20such%20as%20speaking%20at%20conferences%20and%20hosting%20tech%20podcasts%2C%20and%20she%20has%20learned%20how%20to%20set%20better%20work-life%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20her%20compensation%20is%20about%20%24130%2C000%20annually%2C%20including%20stock%20units%20and%20bonuses.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20work%20history%20and%20current%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20or%20finance%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%20journey%3F%20Please%20reach%20out%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ashubhangigoel%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eshubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C