0researcher%20has%20announced%20their%20resignation%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-competition-investor-anxiety-talent-retention-microsoft-meta-google-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOpenAI%2520first%2520launched%2520in%25202015%2Cfund%2520its%2520capital%252Dintensive%2520mission.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosie%20Campbell%2C%20a%20policy%20researcher%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Substack%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20had%20completed%20her%20final%20week%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20departure%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20resignation%20in%20October%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanother-safety-researcher-is-leaving-openai-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiles%20Brundage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20policy%20advisor%20who%20headed%20the%20AGI%20Readiness%20team.%20Following%20his%20departure%2C%20the%20AGI%20Readiness%20team%20disbanded%2C%20and%20its%20members%20dispersed%20across%20different%20sectors%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AGI%20Readiness%20team%20advised%20the%20company%20on%20the%20world's%20capacity%20to%20safely%20manage%20AGI%2C%20a%20theoretical%20version%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20could%20someday%20equal%20or%20surpass%20human%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20post%2C%20Campbell%20echoed%20Brundage's%20reason%20for%20leaving%2C%20citing%20a%20desire%20for%20more%20freedom%20to%20address%20issues%20that%20impacted%20the%20entire%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20been%20strongly%20driven%20by%20the%20mission%20of%20ensuring%20safe%20and%20beneficial%20AGI%20and%20after%20Miles's%20departure%20and%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20AGI%20Readiness%20team%2C%20I%20believe%20I%20can%20pursue%20this%20more%20effectively%20externally%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20OpenAI%20remains%20at%20the%2