20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733073966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674b73a5fa0140cdd5664c83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-founder-redwood-materials-ev-battery-recycling-startup-revenue-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20founder%20JB%20Straubel%20says%20his%20recycled%20EV%20battery%20company%20aims%20to%20produce%20enough%20batteries%20for%201%20million%20electric%20vehicles%20annually.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-founder-redwood-materials-ev-battery-recycling-startup-revenue-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Children%20Among%205%20Who%20Died%20Of%20Heart%20Attack%20Within%2025%20Days%20In%20Aligarh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChildren%20aged%2014%20and%208%20-%20a%20boy%20and%20a%20girl%20-%20are%20among%20the%20five%20people%20who%20died%20of%20heart%20attack%20within%2025%20days%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Chaudhary%2C%20of%20Arana%20village%2C%20used%20to%20go%20on%20a%20daily%20run%20as%20she%20was%20preparing%20for%20a%20physical%20test%20for%20a%20constable's%20job%20in%20the%20state%20police.%20On%20November%2023%2C%20while%20running%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20she%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20collapsed.%20She%20was%2020.%20The%20doctors%20at%20the%20JN%20medical%20college%20said%20that%20she%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20covered%20some%204-5%20rounds%20of%20the%20ground.%20Thereafter%2C%20she%20collapsed%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jaykumar%2C%20Mamata's%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohit%20Chaudhary%2C%20from%20Sirauli%20village%2C%20was%20a%20student%20of%20Class%206.%20The%2014-year-old%20boy%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20annual%20sports%20day%20competition.%20During%20a%20practice%20run%20on%20Friday%2C%20he%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20died%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20eight-year-old%20Diksha%2C%20a%20Lodhi%20Nagar%20resident%2C%20while%20playing%20with%20her%20friends%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20November%205%2C%20pediatrician%20Dr%20Lavnish%20Aggarwal%20went%20for%20his%20regular%20morning%20walk%20and%20returned%20home.%20As%20he%20was%20getting%20ready%20for%20work%2C%20he%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-nine-year-old%20Saiyad%20Barkat%20Haider%20died%20in%20his%20sleep%20on%20November%2020.%20The%20reason%3A%20a%20massive%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20slept%20at%20night%20and%20when%20I%20did%20not%20hear%20him%20snore%2C%20I%20checked%20up%20on%20him.%20I%20realised%20he%20is%20dead.%20The%20doctors%20said%20he%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmad%20Mustafa%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20cousin%20of%20Saiyad%20Barkat%20Haider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20city%20cardiologist%20said%20that%20cases%20of%20heart%20attacks%20have%20increased%20since%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20two%20to%20three%20years%20after%20Covid%2C%20it%20has%20been%20seen%20that%20cases%20of%20heart%20attacks%20have%20increased%20among%20young%20people.%20Stress%20was%20a%20big%20factor%20in%20such%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Asar%20Kamal%2C%20Cardiologist%2C%20Kamal%20Heart%20Care%20Centre%20in%20Aligarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAligarh's%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%20Neeraj%20Tyagi%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20the%20deaths%20but%20stressed%20on%20taking%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20M%20Rabbani%2C%20of%20the%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%2C%20said%20deaths%20by%20cardiac%20arrest%20has%20increased%20by%2022%25%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20healthy%20person%20dies%20within%20an%20hour%2C%20it%20is%20called%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrest.%20It%20has%20increased%20by%2022%20percent%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20Mostly%20this%20reason%20is%20heart%20attack.%20However%2C%20some%20children%20have%20congenital%20heart%20disease.%20If%20it%20is%20not%20examined%2C%20further%20damage%20may%20occur.%20If%20a%20child%20complains%20of%20shortness%20of%20breath%20and%20chest%20pain%2C%20it%20should%20be%20examined%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20professor%20M%20Rabbani%2C%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20research%20conducted%20a%20study.%20There%20was%20no%20increase%20in%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrest%20due%20to%20vaccination%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data.%20But%20those%20who%20were%20seriously%20affected%20by%20Covid%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20heart%20attack%20increases%20in%20them.%20Such%20people%20must%20get%20themselves%20screened%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20some%20minor%20tests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20professor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Adnan%20Khan)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733073720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fjlv1a6qg_aligarh-deaths-_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-children-among-5-who-died-of-heart-attack-within-25-days-in-aligarh-7149768%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Children%20aged%2014%20and%208%20-%20a%20boy%20and%20a%20girl%20-%20are%20among%20the%20five%20people%20who%20died%20of%20heart%20attack%20within%2025%20days%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-children-among-5-who-died-of-heart-attack-within-25-days-in-aligarh-7149768%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Syrian%20government%20loses%20control%20of%20second-larges