ting%20an%20unnamed%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20news%20%C2%A0Prsss%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported%20that%20the%20name%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20has%20been%20finalised%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra.%20The%20meeting%20to%20elect%20him%20as%20the%20new%20BJP%20legislature%20party%20leader%20will%20be%20held%20on%20December%202%20or%203.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20outgoing%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20reiterated%20that%20he%20would%20support%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20--%20a%20declaration%20he%20had%20made%20on%20Wednesday.%20But%20till%20date%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%20is%20the%20people's%20government.%20I%20have%20clarified%20my%20role.%20The%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20honourable%20Home%20Minister%20will%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20(Chief%20Minister).%20They%20(BJP%20MLAs)%20are%20meeting%20tomorrow.%20It%20will%20be%20decided.%20Don't%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20ahead%20of%20a%20key%20meeting%20with%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20sources%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20be%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20he%20would%20have%20two%20deputies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20announcement%20has%20drawn%20jibes%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20leader%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%3A%26quot%3Binsult%26quot%3B%20to%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20rules%20only%20apply%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20while%20rules%20don't%20for%20some%20special%20ones.%20To%20declare%20the%20swearing%20in%20date%2C%20unilaterally%2C%20without%20even%20staking%20claim%20to%20form%20government%20and%20show%20numbers%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20Governor%2C%20is%20pure%20anarchy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20alliance%20Mahayuti%20had%20won%20a%20whopping%20230%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20state%20election.%20The%20BJP%20led%20with%20132%20seats%2C%20giving%20it%20claim%20to%20the%20top%20job%2C%20while%20Mr%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20got%2057%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2041.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733072460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fv1qi22mg_devendra-fadnavis-poster_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-election-2024-posters-demanding-devendra-fadnavis-as-chief-minister-up-in-nagpur-7149417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20demand%20for%20naming%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20is%20growing.%20This%20time%2C%20posters%20have%20come%20up%20in%20Nagpur%20reinforcing%20the%20demand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-election-2024-posters-demanding-devendra-fadnavis-as-chief-minister-up-in-nagpur-7149417%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Equity%20boom%20spurs%20shareholder%20activism%2C%20reshapes%20corporate%20boardrooms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733072441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fequity-boom-spurs-shareholder-activism-reshapes-corporate-boardrooms-124120100124_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Large%20investors%20now%20assert%20their%20right%20to%20have%20a%20say%20in%20investee%20companies%2C%20underscore%20analysts%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fequity-boom-spurs-shareholder-activism-reshapes-corporate-boardrooms-124120100124_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thrashed%20For%20Being%20Indian'%3A%20Kolkata%20Resident%20Narrates%20Bangladesh%20Ordeal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20youth%20from%20Kolkata%20said%20he%20was%20thrashed%20in%20Dhaka%20by%20unidentified%20people%20after%20they%20learnt%20he%20was%20a%20Hindu%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayan%20Ghosh%2C%2022%2C%20from%20Belgharia%20in%20the%20northern%20fringes%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20had%20gone%20to%20Bangladesh%20on%20November%2023%20and%20stayed%20at%20a%20friend's%20place%2C%20and%20the%20family%20treated%20him%20as%20their%20own%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20as%20me%20and%20my%20friend%20went%20out%20for%20a%20stroll%20late%20in%20the%20evening%20on%20November%2026%2C%20a%20group%20of%20four-five%20youths%20accosted%20me%20around%2070%20metres%20from%20my%20friend's%20house.%20They%20asked%20me%20about%20my%20identity.%20As%20I%20told%20them%20I%20was%20from%20India%20and%20a%20Hindu%2C%20they%20started%20kicking%20and%20punching%20me%20and%20even%20attacked%20my%20friend%20who%20tried%20to%20save%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20told%20PTI%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20even%20snatched%20my%20mobile%20phone%20and%20wallet%20at%20knifepoint.%20No%20bystander%20came%20to%20our%20rescue.%20There%20was%20no%20policeman%20nearby.%20After%20the%20incident%2C%20we%20went%20to%20Shyampur%20police%20station%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20lodge%20any%20complaint.%20Instead%2C%20they%20repeatedly%20asked%20me%20why%20I%20visited%20Bangladesh.%20After%20I%20showed%20them%20my%20passport%20and%20visa%2C%20and%20after%20speaking%20to%20my%20friend%20and%20his%20family%20members%2C%20they%20were%20satisfied%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20my%20wounds%20treated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ghosh%20said%20he%20was%20denied%20treatment%20at%20two%20private%20medical%20facilities%20and%20finally%20went%20to%20Dhaka%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20treatment%20there%20three%20hours%20after%20the%20incident.%20I%20had%20several%20stitches%20done%20on%20my%20forehead%20and%20head%20and%20even%20had%20injury%20in%20my%20mouth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%2C%20still%20struck%20by%20horror%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20finally%20file%20a%20complaint%20with%20Belgharia%20police%20station%20upon%20his%20return%20to%20Kolkata%20on%20November%2030%20as%20neither%20the%20immigration%20nor%20Bangladesh%20Border%20Guards%20at%20Darshana%20border%20outpost%20registered%20his%20complaint%20officially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20too%20scared%20to%20visit%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Dhaka%20fearing%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20me%20and%20my%20friend's%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20staying%20at%20his%20friend's%20house%20for%20three%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Mr%20Ghosh%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20by%20his%20friend%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20November%2029%20and%20he%20took%20a%20train%20for%20Darshana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Darshana%2C%20he%20crossed%20over%20to%20Gede%2C%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%20in%20the%20morning%20of%20November%2029%20and%20took%20a%20Sealdah-bound%20local%20train%20to%20reach%20Belgharia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%2C%20who%20wished%20that%20the%20issue%20not%20be%20politicised%2C%20said%20he%20intended%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Bangladesh%20Deputy%20High%20Commission%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20youths%20were%20locals%20having%20some%20connections%20and%20probably%20that%20is%20why%20the%20police%20did%20not%20initiate%20any%20action%20against%20them%20and%20did%20not%20lodge%20my%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20not%20imagine%20such%20a%20nightmarish%20situation%20awaiting%20me%20in%20a%20neighbouring%20country%20where%20people%20speak%20the%20same%20language%20as%20us%20and%20share%20similar%20food%20habits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bangladesh%20Deputy%20High%20Commission%20official%20said%20the%20interim%20government%20was%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20every%20citizen%2C%20from%20all%20communities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tourists%20and%20will%20look%20into%20complaints%20once%20filed%20for%20fair%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733072160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F1tb27fp8_bangladesh_625x300_01_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthrashed-for-being-indian-kolkata-resident-narrates-bangladesh-ordeal-7149258%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20youth%20from%20Kolkata%20said%20he%20was%20thrashed%20in%20Dhaka%20by%20unidentified%20people%20after%20they%20learnt%20he%20was%20a%20Hindu%20from%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthrashed-for-being-indian-kolkata-resident-narrates-bangladesh-ordeal-7149258%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Triptii%20enjoys%20bike%20ride%20with%20boyfriend%20Sam%20Merchant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733071812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115872761%2Cimgsize-49392.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftriptii-dimri-enjoys-a-sunday-evening-bike-ride-with-rumoured-boyfriend-sam-merchant-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F115872761.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftim