2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%C2%A0teenage%20girl%20from%20Chiba%20Prefecture%20climbed%20over%20a%202.5-meter%20glass%20barrier%20on%20the%2012th%20floor%20and%20jumped%20from%20the%20west%20side%20of%20the%20building.%20She%20landed%20on%2032-year-old%20Chikako%20Chiba%2C%20who%20was%20walking%20with%20friends.%20Both%20were%20rushed%20to%20a%20local%20hospital%2C%20where%20the%20teenage%20girl%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20within%20an%20hour.%20Chiba%20also%20died%20of%20her%20injuries%20later%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20initial%20investigation%20suggested%20that%20the%20student%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%20although%20the%20motive%20was%20unclear.%20Yokohama%20police%20submitted%20the%20case%20to%20prosecutors%2C%20recommending%20that%20an%20indictment%20be%20recorded.%20The%20police%20argued%20that%20the%2017-year-old%20girl%20was%20of%20an%20age%20where%20she%20could%20reasonably%20understand%20that%20her%20actions%20might%20cause%20harm%20to%20others.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20dead%20teenager%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20%26quot%3Bgross%20negligence%20resulting%20in%20death%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20state%20broadcaster%20NHK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0decision%20has%20been%20widely%20debated%20on%20social%20media.%20Many%20said%C2%A0that%20pursuing%20charges%20against%20the%20dead%20teenager%20is%20unnecessary%20and%20a%20misallocation%20of%20resources%2C%20as%20it%20serves%20no%20practical%20purpose.%20However%2C%20legal%20experts%20suggest%20that%20although%20the%20girl%20cannot%20be%20held%20legally%20accountable%20for%20the%20charge%20of%20gross%20negligence%20resulting%20in%20death%2C%20pursuing%20prosecution%20could%20have%20implications%20for%20potential%20civil%20claims%20filed%20by%20the%20victim's%20family.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20may%20serve%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20others%2C%20cautioning%20against%20actions%20that%20endanger%20innocent%20lives%20during%20suicide%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3