o%20Varanasi's%20Kaal%20Bhairav%20temple%20and%20recorded%20a%20video%20of%20her%20cutting%20a%20cake%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20The%20video%2C%20now%20in%20wide%20circulation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20is%20receiving%20sharp%20criticism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fvideo-woman-cuts-cake-inside-varanasi-temple-sparks-outrage-7147679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Difference%20In%20India%20And%20Bangladesh%20If...'%3A%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20On%20Minorities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20comments%20comparing%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20on%20how%20they%20treat%20minorities%20have%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20Calling%20the%20November%2024%20Sambhal%20incident%20unfortunate%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20compare%20the%20situation%20of%20minorities%20in%20India%20with%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20afraid%20that%20the%20situation%20which%20was%20during%201947%2C%20we%20are%20being%20taken%20towards%20that%20direction.%20When%20the%20youth%20talk%20of%20jobs%2C%20they%20don't%20get%20it.%20We%20don't%20have%20good%20hospitals%2C%20education...%20They%20are%20not%20improving%20the%20condition%20of%20roads%20but%20are%20trying%20to%20demolish%20the%20mosque%20in%20search%20of%20a%20temple.%20The%20Sambhal%20incident%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20Some%20were%20working%20in%20shops%20and%20were%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Mufti%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20many%20injured%20in%20clashes%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Sambhal%20during%20a%20court-ordered%20survey%20of%20Shahi%20Jama%20Masjid.%20The%20mosque%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20legal%20battle%20after%20some%20petitions%20claimed%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20connection%20that%20a%20local%20court%20ordered%20its%20survey.%20The%20local%20residents%20opposed%20the%20survey%20and%20the%20situation%20snowballed%20into%20full-blown%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20brought%20up%20a%20similar%20controversy%20involving%20the%20dargah%20of%20Sufi%20saint%20Moinuddin%20Chishti%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Ajmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAjmer%20Sharif%20Dargah%20where%20people%20from%20all%20religions%20offer%20prayers%20is%20the%20biggest%20example%20of%20brotherhood.%20Now%20they%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20dig%20into%20it%20to%20search%20for%20a%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Mufti%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20court%20notices%20to%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Centre%20following%20a%20petition%20that%20claimed%20there%20was%20a%20Shiva%20temple%20in%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20Dargah.%20The%20petition%2C%20filed%20in%20September%2C%20has%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20allow%20worship%20at%20the%20spot%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mufti%20then%20went%20on%20to%20compare%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20on%20how%20they%20treat%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20atrocities%20are%20being%20committed%20on%20Hindus.%20If%20atrocities%20are%20committed%20on%20minorities%20in%20India%20also%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%3F%20I%20don't%20find%20any%20difference%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20diplomatic%20row%20has%20erupted%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20after%20Hindu%20priest%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness%20(ISKCON)%2C%20was%20arrested%20from%20Dhaka's%20Hazrat%20Shahjalal%20International%20Airport%20on%20Monday.%20Mr%20Das%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20Sammilita%20Sanatani%20Jagran%20Jote%2C%20was%20denied%20bail%20and%20sent%20to%20jail%20in%20a%20sedition%20case%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20triggered%20clashes%20between%20his%20supporters%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20situation%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minority%20groups%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20visuals%20of%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%20Many%20shows%20young%20people%20in%20Bangladesh%20stomping%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20In%20the%20latest%20attack%2C%20three%20Hindu%20temples%20were%20vandalised%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20Friday%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Chattogram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20atrocities%20against%20Hindu%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20images%20of%20the%20Indian%20flag%20being%20disrespected%20there%20has%20created%20a%20tense%20atmosphere%20between%20the%20two%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20in%20a%20statement%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20halt%20to%20atrocities%20against%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%20Noting%20the%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20minorities%2C%20India%20has%20said%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Muhammad%20Yunus-led%20interim%20government%20to%20protect%20the%20life%20and%20liberty%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733059800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqdsvr6c_mehbooba-mufti_625x300_28_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-difference-in-india-and-bangladesh-if-what-mehbooba-mufti-said-on-minorities-7148464%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti's%20comments%20comparing%20Ind