ent%20shopping%20mall-cum-entertainment%20centre%20is%20now%20located%20just%204%20km%20away%20and%20hundreds%20of%20residential%20colonies%20have%20cropped%20up%20on%20the%20then%20vacant%20land%20near%20the%20disaster%20site%2C%20overlooking%20pollution%20that%20the%20tragedy%20created%20-%20be%20it%20groundwater%20or%20soil%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highly%20toxic%20methyl%20isocyanate%20gas%20leaked%20from%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20India%20Limited%20(UCIL)%20plant%20here%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20December%202%20and%203%2C%201984%2C%20killing%205%2C479%20persons%20and%20maiming%20more%20than%20five%20lakh%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Kali%20Parade%20industrial%20campus%20and%20it%20was%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20present-day%20old%20city%2C%20Vishnu%20Rathore%2C%20a%20former%20corporator%20who%20had%20represented%20the%20adjoining%20areas%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we%20can%20say%20it%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20city%20as%20hundreds%20of%20residential%20colonies%20and%20shopping%20outlets%20catering%20to%20the%20people's%20needs%20have%20come%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathore%2C%20who%20was%2016%20years'%20old%20at%20the%20time%20of%20disaster%2C%20said%20the%20area%20is%20still%20under-developed%20but%20the%20real%20estate%20business%20has%20been%20thriving%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20of%20the%20abandoned%20factory%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20tragedy%2C%20the%20city%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20population%20growth%20and%20urban%20development%2C%20including%20in%20areas%20surrounding%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20plant%20campus%2C%20Confederation%20of%20Real%20Estate%20Developers'%20Associations%20of%20India%20(CREDAI)%20Bhopal%20unit%20chief%20Manoj%20Singh%20Meek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20area%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Union%20Carbide%2C%20located%20in%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20city%2C%20must%20have%20added%20around%20100%20residential%20colonies%20and%20a%20population%20of%20three%20lakh%20during%20the%20past%20four%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20industrial%20disaster%20severely%20dented%20Bhopal's%20development%20and%20economic%20growth%2C%20Meek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20this%20disaster%2C%20Bhopal%20lagged%20behind%20in%20the%20race%20of%20development%20of%20state%20capitals.%20No%20new%20industrial%20and%20big%20business%20development%20took%20place%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20resulting%20in%20slow%20pace%20of%20the%20city's%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Meek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20gas%20tragedy%2C%20Bhopal's%20population%20was%20around%208.5%20lakh.%20Nearly%205.2%20lakh%20persons%2C%20including%202%20lakh%20children%20and%20about%203%2C000%20pregnant%20women%2C%20were%20then%20residing%20in%20the%2036%20wards%20which%20were%20later%20designated%20as%20%26quot%3Bgas-affected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20disaster%20saw%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20people%20leaving%20the%20city%20due%20to%20health%20concerns%20and%20fear%20of%20lingering%20contamination%2C%20Meek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20time%2C%20the%20population%20stabilised%20and%20began%20to%20grow%2C%20influenced%20by%20factors%20like%20urbanisation%20and%20economic%20opportunities%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201991%2C%20the%20population%20grew%2C%20indicating%20a%20gradual%20return%20and%20influx%20of%20residents%2C%20Meek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20development%20in%20the%20immediate%20vicinity%20of%20the%20gas%20leak%20site%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcautious%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20lingering%20contamination%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plant%20site%20remains%20largely%20abandoned%2C%20with%20limited%20residential%20or%20commercial%20projects%20directly%20adjacent%20to%20it%2C%20the%20CREDAI%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20urban%20expansion%20and%20population%20pressure%20in%20peripheral%20areas%20have%20spurred%20development%20in%20neighbourhoods%20further%20from%20the%20plant%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chairman%20of%20the%20Institute%20of%20Town%20Planners%20India%20(ITPI)%2C%20MP%20Chapter%2C%20Shubhashis%20Banerjee%20said%20most%20of%20the%20residential%20development%20adjacent%20to%20Union%20Carbide%20has%20been%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20compensation%20disbursed%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%20tragedy%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20local%20economy%2C%20resulting%20in%20small-ticket%20size%20illegal%20real%20estate%20development%20in%20surrounding%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gas%20leak%20site%20was%20not%20dealt%20with%20properly%2C%20unlike%20Hiroshima%20in%20Japan%2C%20which%20faced%20an%20atomic%20bomb%20attack%2C%20he%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20handle%20the%20catastrophe%20site%20properly.%20The%20project%20for%20the%20memorial%20was%20prepared%20but%20could%20not%20be%20implemented.%20A%20world%20class%20memorial%20should%20have%20been%20developed%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20said%20the%20tragedy%20alerted%20the%20government%20to%20strengthen%20the%20environmental%20rules%20and%20safety%20measures%20for%20the%20hazardous%20industry%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20slowed%20the%20pace%20of%20industrialisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERachna%20Dhingra%20of%20the%20Bhopal%20Group%20for%20Information%20and%20Action%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20gas%20survivors%2C%20said%20development%20took%20place%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%20after%20the%20construction%20of%20an%20overbridge%20parallel%20to%20Union%20Carbide%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overbridge%20was%20constructed%20on%20the%20solar%20evaporation%20ponds%20of%20Union%20Carbide%20where%20the%20toxic%20waste%20was%20being%20dumped.%20After%20that%2C%20large-scale%20real%20estate%20development%20took%20place%20in%20neighbouring%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20part%20of%20the%20solar%20evaporation%20pond%20has%20been%20encroached%20upon%2C%20Dhingra%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20shift%20the%20settlements%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20campus%20and%20the%20Centre%20had%20sanctioned%20Rs%2040%20crore%2C%20but%20the%20proposal%20was%20shelved%20and%20situation%20became%20grimmer%20later%20on%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20and%20groundwater%20in%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20have%20turned%20toxic%2C%20but%20the%20people%20are%20living%20in%20such%20conditions%2C%20Dhingra%20said%2C%20while%20blaming%20politicians%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bmess%26quot%3B%20around%20the%20gas%20leak%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733055240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F2p93cueg_bhopal-gas-tragedy-getty_625x300_14_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonce-shunned-areas-near-bhopal-gas-tragedy-site-now-seeing-real-estate-boom-7147631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Carbide%20factory%2C%20the%20site%20of%20the%20deadly%20gas%20leak%2040%20years%20ago%20which%20was%20once%20located%20on%20Bhopal's%20outskirts%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20ostracised%20with%20its%20neighbourhood%20now%20dotted%20with%20residential%20and%20commercial%20establishments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonce-shunned-areas-near-bhopal-gas-tragedy-site-now-seeing-real-estate-boom-7147631%22%2C%22cdnAmpU