0confusion%20when%20I%20have%20already%20made%20my%20stand%20clear%20last%20week%3F%20I%20have%20already%20said%20the%20decision%20on%20CM's%20post%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20will%20be%20acceptable%20to%20me%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20will%20have%20my%20full%20backing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Sena%20chief%20was%20in%20Satara%2C%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20president%20Chandrashekar%20Bawankule%20announced%20that%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20the%20new%20Mahayuti%20government%20will%20take%20place%20in%20south%20Mumbai's%20Azad%20Maidan%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20pick.%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20the%20state's%20tallest%20BJP%20leader%20and%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20frontrunner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20Assembly%20election%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20were%20declared%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Mahayuti%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win%2C%20scoring%20230%20seats%20in%20the%20288-member%20Assembly.%20The%20Opposition%20bloc%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20managed%20to%20win%20just%2046%20seats%2C%20months%20after%20its%20good%20show%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20won%20132%20seats%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20claim%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20After%20days%20of%20political%20posturing%20by%20a%20section%20of%20Sena%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20cleared%20the%20air%20and%20said%20he%20would%20not%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bobstacle%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20accept%20the%20BJP%20leadership's%20decision%20on%20the%20next%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20Sena%20chief's%20announcement%20must%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20BJP's%20strong%20score%20in%20this%20election.%20The%20BJP%20now%20needs%20only%20one%20of%20its%20allies%20to%20reach%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20Assembly%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20has%20backed%20it%20in%20the%20Chief%20M