C231.49%20in%20Chennai.%20The%20revised%20rates%20have%20kicked%20in%20from%20today%2C%20dealing%20a%20major%20blow%20to%20the%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuel%20expenses%20are%20a%20key%20component%20that%20determines%20the%20cost%20of%20flight%20tickets.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20second-largest%20cost%20incurred%20for%20operating%20flights%20after%20labour%20costs.%20Fuel%20costs%20squeeze%20profit%20margins%20for%20the%20airlines%20and%20leads%20to%20higher%20ticket%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20oil%20firms%20-%20Bharat%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(BPCL)%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20(IOC)%2C%20and%20Hindustan%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(HPCL)%20-%20revise%20jet%20fuel%20and%20cooking%20gas%20prices%20on%20the%20first%20of%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fget-ready-for-longer-flights-scientists-call-for-slower-planes-to-cut-emissions-6643555%5C%22%3EGet%20Ready%20For%20Longer%20Flights%3A%20Scientists%20Call%20For%20Slower%20Planes%20To%20Cut%20Emissions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20companies%20had%20last%20raised%20ATF%20prices%20on%20November%201%20after%20two%20rounds%20of%20monthly%20reduction%20by%20Rs%205%2C883%20per%20kilolitre%20on%20October%201%20and%20by%20Rs%204%2C495.5%20on%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rates%20of%20commercial%20LPG%20-%20used%20in%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20-%20have%20also%20been%20increased%20for%20the%20fifth%20time%20in%20a%20row.%20It%20is%20now%20costlier%20by%20Rs%2016.5%20per%2019-kg%20cylinder%20and%20is%20available%20at%20Rs%201818.50%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Rs%201771%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Rs%201%2C927%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Rs%201%2C980%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20by%20Rs%20172.5%20per%20cylinder%20in%20the%20five%20monthly%20increases%20from%20August%2C%20which%20follow%20four%20rounds%20of%20price%20reductions%2C%20amounting%20to%20a%20total%20price%20cut%20of%20Rs%20148%20per%20cylinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commercial%20LPG%20rates%20are%20now%20at%20their%20highest%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20or%20cooking%20gas%20remains%20unchanged%20at%20Rs%20803%20per%2014.2-kg%20cylinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733044440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fu3qopdfo_plane-generic-unsplash_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-tickets-may-get-costlier-as-oil-companies-raise-aviation-fuel-prices-7146727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Flight%20tickets%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20costlier%20with%20oil%20companies%20announcing%20a%20hike%20in%20aviation%20fuel%20prices.%20The%20cost%20of%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%20(ATF)%20has%20been%20hiked%20by%20Rs%201%2C318%20per%20kilolitre%2C%20a%20month%20after%20it%20was%20raised%20by%20Rs%202%2C941.5%20or%203.3%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-tickets-may-get-costlier-as-oil-companies-raise-aviation-fuel-prices-7146727%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanta%20Sarma%20Ready%20To%20Ban%20Beef%20In%20Assam%20If%20Congress%20Asks%20For%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20allegation%20that%20BJP%20distributed%20beef%20to%20win%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20Samaguri%2C%20which%20was%20under%20Congress%20control%20for%20five%20consecutive%20terms%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20he%20was%20happy%20that%20the%20opposition%20party%20raised%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSamaguri%20was%20with%20Congress%20for%2025%20years.%20Congress%20losing%20a%20constituency%20like%20Samaguri%20by%2027%2C000%20votes%20(sic)%20is%20the%20biggest%20shame%20in%20its%20history.%20It%20is%20Congress's%20defeat%20more%20than%20BJP's%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20after%20a%20party%20meeting%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Diplu%20Ranjan%20Sarmah%20defeated%20Congress'%20Tanzil%2C%20son%20of%20party%20MP%20Rakibul%20Hussain%2C%20by%2024%2C501%20votes%20in%20a%20bypoll%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20amidst%20sadness%2C%20Rakibul%20Hussain%20said%20one%20good%20thing%20that%20eating%20beef%20is%20wrong%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20He%20said%20that%20it%20was%20wrong%20for%20Congress-BJP%20to%20win%20elections%20by%20offering%20beef%20to%20voters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20MP's%20reported%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20know%20if%20Congress%20was%20winning%20Samaguri%20by%20offering%20beef%20to%20voters.%20He%20knows%20Samaguri%20very%20well.%20Does%20it%20mean%20that%20Samaguri%20can%20be%20won%20by%20offering%20beef%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20Mr%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hussain%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Dhubri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20this%20year%20by%20a%20record%20margin%20of%20over%2010.12%20lakh%20votes%2C%20was%20an%20MLA%20from%20Samaguri%20for%20five%20consecutive%20terms%20before%20becoming%20a%20parliamentarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20Rakibul%20Hussain%20that%20beef%20should%20be%20banned%20as%20he%20himself%20said%20it%20is%20wrong.%20He%20only%20needs%20to%20give%20me%20in%20writing%20that%20neither%20BJP%20nor%20Congress%20should%20speak%20about%20beef%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20should%20be%20banned%20in%20Assam.%20If%20we%20do%20that%2C%20all%20problems%20will%20be%20solved%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20further%20said%20that%20he%20would%20write%20to%20the%20state%20Congress%20president%20about%20his%20stand%20on%20beef%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Hussain's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20will%20write%20to%20Bhupen%20Borah%20and%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20also%20advocates%20banning%20beef%20in%20line%20with%20Rakibul%20Hussain%2C%20and%20just%20inform%20me.%20I%20will%20ban%20beef%20completely%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20(accordingly).%20Then%20BJP%2C%20AGP%2C%20CPM%2C%20nobody%20will%20be%20able%20to%20offer%2C%20and%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20all%20should%20stop%20eating%20beef%2C%20and%20all%20problems%20will%20be%20solved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20that%20Rakibul%20Hussain%20has%20made%20this%20statement%20because%20at%20least%20one%20step%20has%20been%20taken.%20Now%2C%20the%20second%20step%20should%20be%20taken%20by%20Bhupen%20Borah%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20of%20beef%20is%20not%20illegal%20in%20Assam%2C%20but%20The%20Assam%20Cattle%20Preservation%20Act%20of%202021%20bans%20cattle%20slaughter%20and%20sale%20of%20beef%20in%20areas%20where%20Hindus%2C%20Jains%20and%20Sikhs%20are%20in%20majority%20and%20within%20a%20five-km%20radius%20of%20a%20temple%20or%20satra%20(Vaishnavite%20monastery).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733043480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Flvnebul8_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_28_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimanta-sarma-ready-to-ban-beef-in-assam-if-congress-asks-for-it-7146863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Responding%20to%20the%20allegation%20that%20BJP%20distributed%20beef%20to%20win%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20Samaguri%2C%20which%20was%20under%20Congress%20control%20for%20five%20consecutive%20terms%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20he%20was%20happy%20that%20the%20opposition%20party%20raised%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimanta-sarma-ready-to-ban-beef-in-assam-if-congress-asks-for-it-7146863%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMadam%20Is%20Busy%26quot%3B%3A%20When%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20Kept%20Najma%20Heptulla%20Waiting%20For%20An%20Hour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20Inter-Parliamentary%20Union%20(IPU)%20in%201999%2C%20Najma%20Heptulla%20rang%20up%20the%20then%20Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20from%20Berlin%20to%20convey%20the%20news%20but%20had%20to%20hold%20the%20phone%20line%20for%20an%20hour%20as%20staff%20told%20her%20that%20%26quot%3BMadam%20is%20busy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20deputy%20chairperson%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20who%20had%20left%20the%20Congress%20after%20reported%20differences%20with%20Ms%20Gandhi%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202004%2C%20mentions%20this%20incident%20in%20her%20just-released%20autobiography%20%26quot%3BIn%20Pursuit%20of%20Democracy%3A%20Beyond%20Party%20Lines%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Heptulla%20says%20the%20IPU%20presidency%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20first%20and%20a%20great%20honour%2C%20marking%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20my%20journey%20from%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20to%20the%20world%20parliamentary%20stage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20she%20telephoned%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20from%20Berlin%20and%20he%20received%20her%20call%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20heard%20the%20news%2C%20he%20was%20delighted%2C%20first%20because%20the%20honour%20had%20come%20to%20India%2C%20and%20second%2C%20it%20had%20come%20to%20an%20Indian%20Muslim%20woman.%20He%20said%2C%20'You%20come%20back%20and%20we%20will%20celebrate.'%20I%20could%20also%20connect%20to%20the%20vice-presidential%20office%20instantly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20she%20%26quot%3Brang%20up%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Congress%20Party%20President%20and%20my%20leader%2C%20one%20of%20her%20staff%20first%20said%2C%20'Madam%20is%20busy.'%20When%20I%20pointed%20out%20that%20I%20was%20calling%20from%20Berlin%2C%20an%20international%20call%2C%20he%20just%20said%2C%20'Please%20hold%20the%20line.'%20I%20waited%20for%20one%20full%20hour.%20Sonia%20never%20came%20on%20the%20line%20to%20speak%20to%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Heptulla%20says%20she%20was%20truly%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%20call%2C%20I%20did%20not%20tell%20her%20anything.%20Before%20forwarding%20my%20name%20for%20the%20post%20of%20IPU%20President%2C%20I%20had%20taken%20her%20permission%2C%20and%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20had%20given%20her%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20governor%20of%20Manipur%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20every%20country%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20family%20has%20its%20special%20moments%20-%20events%20so%20important%2C%20and%20somehow%20so%20personal%2C%20that%20they%20transcend%20the%20normal%20flow%20of%20daily%20life%20-%20this%20was%20one%20such%20moment%20for%20me%20-%20a%20moment%20in%20time%20of%20such%20importance%20that%20it%20drilled%20a%20sense%20of%20rejection%20in%20my%20psyche%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%2C%20however%2C%20a%20rejection%20that%20proved%20prescient.%20It%20prophesied%20a%20time%20of%20transition%2C%20a%20downward%20spiral%20and%20crisis%20in%20the%20Congress%20that%20left%20its%20old-time%20and%20experienced%20members%2C%20who%20had%20given%20their%20all%20to%20the%20party%2C%20beleaguered%20and%20demoralized.%20A%20new%20coterie%20of%20inexperienced%20sycophants%20started%20running%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Heptulla%2C%20who%20was%20made%20the%20Union%20minister%20for%20minority%20affairs%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20of%202014%2C%20says%20after%20she%20became%20the%20IPU%20president%2C%20the%20Vajpayee%20government%20upgraded%20the%20ranking%20of%20her%20office%20from%20minister%20of%20state%20to%20cabinet%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAtalji%20allocated%201%20crore%20in%20the%20Budget%20for%20the%20IPU%20president%20to%20travel%20to%20countries%20not%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20IPU%20Council.%20It%20was%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20who%20invited%20me%20and%20other%20MPs%20to%20celebrate%20my%20election%20as%20IPU%20President%20at%20the%20Parliament%20Annex%2C%20where%20we%20generally%20host%20all%20our%20Parliament%20receptions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20book%2C%20published%20by%20Rupa%2C%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20following%20year%2C%20when%20I%20invited%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20to%20attend%20the%20Millennium%20Conference%20of%20Presiding%20Officers%20in%20New%20York%2C%20she%20opted%20out%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Heptulla%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20her%20political%20career%2C%20Ms%20Heptulla%20authored%20several%20books%20and%20is%20a%20prominent%20advocate%20for%20democracy%2C%20social%20justice%2C%20and%20women's%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20in%201998%2C%20when%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20donned%20the%20party%20mantle%2C%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20many%20layers%20of%20people%20sprung%20up%20between%20the%20rank%20and%20file%2C%20and%20the%20leader%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20problem%20with%2010%20Janpath.%20Direct%20communication%20was%20cut%20off%20because%20of%20junior%20functionaries.%20They%20were%20not%20party%20workers%2C%20just%20clerks%20and%20other%20staff%20working%20there.%20And%20they%20blocked%20all%20access%20to%20the%20leader%2C%20affecting%20organizational%20health%20and%20ethics%2C%20compromising%20both%20harmony%20and%20productivity%20of%20the%20party%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Heptulla%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Congress%20followers%2C%20we%20no%20longer%20had%20an%20active%20role%20in%20providing%20feedback%20to%20our%20leader%20-%20so%20critical%20for%20a%20party%20to%20perform%20well.%20There%20was%20little%20interaction%20based%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20exchanges%2C%20little%20understanding%20of%20who%20were%20part%20of%20our%20leader's%20in-groups%20or%20out-groups%20or%20even%20how%20to%20support%20our%20leader's%20vision.%20The%20decline%20started%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Heptulla%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20were%20not%20in%20politics%20but%20busy%20with%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20leader's%20behaviour%20was%20counter%20to%20the%20best%20practices%20and%20principles%20of%20collaboration%20that%20had%20evolved%20in%20the%20Congress%20over%20many%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20about%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Heptulla%20says%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20idea%20of%20communication%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsharp%20and%20serious%20departure%20from%20the%20earlier%20Congress%20culture%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIndira%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20keep%20an%20open%20house.%20She%20was%20accessible%20to%20the%20rank-and-file%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733042820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fadisou3o_-najma-heptullah-sonia-gandhi_625x300_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-sonia-gandhi-kept-najma-heptulla-waiting-for-an-hour-over-call-from-berlin-7146407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20being%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20Inter-Parliamentary%20Union%20(IPU)%20in%201999%2C%20Najma%20Heptulla%20rang%20up%20the%20then%20Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20from%20Berlin%20to%20convey%20the%20news%20but%20had%20to%20hold%20the%20phone%20line%20for%20an%20hour%20as%20staff%20told%20her%20that%20%26quot%3BMadam%20is%20busy%26quot