2C%20everything%20is%20done%20by%20volunteers.%20We%20have%20a%20core%20team%2C%20but%20only%20two%20of%20us%20are%20full-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20reached%20over%2030%2C000%20children%20across%20175%20schools%20in%2016%20states.%20The%20group%E2%80%99s%20community%20libraries%20in%20cities%20like%20Kota%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20housing%20more%20than%205%2C000%20books%2C%20recently%20welcomed%20232%20new%20members.%20SABIA%20also%20improved%20library%20spaces%20in%20schools%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Noida%2C%20and%20established%20its%20first%20model%20school%20library%20in%20Jaipur%20that%20houses%20books%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20space%20where%20children%20can%20learn%2C%20creatively%20engage%20themselves%20or%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20organisation%20hosted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311547%2Fdelhi-jasmine-anoop-start-storytelling-initiative-for-children-in-rural-himachal-pradesh-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estorytelling%20sessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20and%20low-budget%20private%20schools%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%2C%20conducted%20by%20a%20team%20of%2014%20storytellers.%20These%20sessions%20focused%20on%20perspective%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20creative%20thinking%2C%20helping%20the%20children%20develop%20important%20life%20skills%20and%20a%20love%20for%20literature.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%2C%20and%20the%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenges%20remain.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20highlighted%20the%20digital%20divide%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20several%20children%20lacking%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20or%20technology%20for%20online%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%2025%2C000%20children%20we%20worked%20with%2C%20only%201%2C000%20could%20sign