e%2C%20embarked%20on%20a%20self-learning%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20farming%20background.%20All%20that%20I%20have%20implemented%20is%20through%20trial-and-error%20and%20self-learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20set%20up%20her%20first%20farm%20in%20Lucknow%20with%2015%20mixed-breed%20cows%2C%20including%20Jerseys%20and%20Sahiwals.%20However%2C%20her%20limited%20knowledge%20of%20cow%20nutrition%20affected%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20milk.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Thane%2C%20Jyoti%20identified%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20pure%20A2%20cow%20milk%20in%20urban%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20getting%20fresh%20milk%20was%20never%20a%20worry.%20When%20my%20daughter%20needed%20pure%20milk%20here%2C%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%2C%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20research%20study%20published%20in%20the%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine%2C%20A2%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20milk%20that%20only%20contains%20a%20variant%20of%20beta-casein%20called%20A2%20%E2%80%94%20has%20on%20several%20occasions%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20lactose%20intolerant%20people.%20The%20difference%20in%20protein%20between%20the%20A2%20and%20A1%20varieties%20makes%20the%20former%20a%20more%20easily%20digestible%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%20to%20dairy%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Jyoti%20established%20Sree%20Balkrishna%20Dairy%20Farm%20(BKD%20Milk)%20on%20two%20acres%20of%20leased%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Maharashtra.%20With%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20she%20envisioned%20a%20farm%20where%20cows%20would%20roam%20freely%2C%20nourished%20by%20organic%20feed%20like%205G%20Napier%20grass%2C%20wheatgrass%2C%20and%20mil