20the%20city.%20We%20need%20a%20collective%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Endolla%20Barcelona%2C%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20electromobility%20network%2C%20the%20use%20of%20EVs%20prevented%20the%20emission%20of%208%2C989%20tons%20of%20CO2%20in%202023.%20Barcelona%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20sustainable%20urban%20development%20with%20improved%20air%20quality.%20The%20city%20sets%20a%20global%20benchmark%20for%20cleaner%20cities%20and%20shows%20how%20sustainable%20urban%20planning%20can%20simultaneously%20improve%20public%20health%2C%20economic%20vitality%2C%20and%20environmental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fd5%2FN1529189.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETransforming%20our%20world%3A%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Published%20on%2021%20October%202015.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732854590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D384037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Learn%20how%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20urban%20planning%2C%20green%20initiatives%2C%20and%20public%20transport%20reforms%20offer%20actionable%20solutions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%20air%20pollution%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384037%2Fbarcelona-air-quality-india-pollution-solution-delhi%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22She%20Gave%20up%20Her%20Own%20Dreams%20for%20Family%2C%20Only%20T