pg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2060%2C%20Aparna%20Das%20has%20helped%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20almost%20100%20people%2C%20from%20children%20to%20the%20elderly.%20She%20has%20consistently%20devoted%20her%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20helping%20others%20because%20she%20found%20joy%20in%20making%20a%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20decades%20ago%2C%20while%20focused%20on%20meeting%20the%20demands%20of%20a%20busy%20joint%20family%2C%20Aparna%20never%20imagined%20that%20one%20day%20she%20would%20be%20shaping%20the%20futures%20of%20so%20many.%20With%20nine%20brothers-in-law%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20mother-in-law%2C%20and%20father-in-law%20to%20care%20for%2C%20Aparna%20often%20felt%20overwhelmed.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20Her%20early%20years%20were%20consumed%20by%20household%20chores%2C%20caregiving%2C%20and%20running%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20work%20that%20made%20me%20sad%2C%20it%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pursue%20the%20things%20I%20loved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20She%20quietly%20embraced%20her%20role%2C%20setting%20aside%20her%20passions%20like%20playing%20the%20guitar%2C%20reading%20books%2C%20and%20following%20her%20own%20interests%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20her%20family.%20But%20as%20the%20years%20went%20by%2C%20a%20subtle%20sense%20of%20disconnection%20from%20her%20true%20self%20began%20to%20take%20root.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20becoming%20a%20mother%20in%201994%2C%20Aparna%20found%20a%20new%20purpose%20in%20raising%20her%20daughter.%20She%20devoted%20herself%20to%20ensuring%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.c