rly%20stages.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20when%20we%20were%20working%20with%20some%20larger%20sellers%2C%20we%20could%20only%20break%20even.%20But%20working%20with%20these%20people%2C%20we%20were%20doing%20well%20for%20ourselves%20and%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rishabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20they%20realised%20that%20industrial%20waste%2C%20particularly%20plastic%2C%20offered%20the%20greatest%20potential%20for%20recycling%20and%20reuse.%20But%20recycling%20plastic%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20complexity%20of%20plastic%20is%20that%20you%20cannot%20intermix%20it.%20Different%20grades%20of%20plastic%20need%20to%20be%20processed%20separately%2C%20so%20that%20the%20end%20product%20is%20actually%20useful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20challenges%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20profits%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20and%20trial-and-error%2C%20the%20company%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20automotive%20industry%2C%20where%20high-grade%20plastic%20is%20used%20for%20manufacturing%20car%20parts.%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20began%20processing%20plastic%20waste%20from%20automotive%20manufacturers%2C%20refining%20their%20segregation%20process%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20plastics%20were%20sorted%20properly%20before%20being%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20thorough%20and%20diligent%20process%2C%20the%20company%20built%20expertise%20in%20plastic%20recycling%2C%20particularly%20in%20turning%20plastic%20waste%20into%20usable%20raw%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20trails%20were%20maddening!%20We%20even%20built%20small%20%3Cem%3Echulas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20experimented%20with%20melting%20small%20amounts%20of%20plastic%20in%20pans%2C%20using%20different%20methods%20at%20a%20very%20small%20scale%20t