3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20modest%20beginning%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20movement%20that%20would%20go%20on%20to%20empower%20tribal%20voices%20through%20storytelling%20and%20visual%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20the%20communication%20gap%20with%20videos%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitesh%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20Rakesh%20Pawara%20(38)%20and%20Arjun%20Pawara%20(37)%2C%20two%20local%20community%20members%20from%20Dhadgaon%20who%20deeply%20understood%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20challenges.%20Together%2C%20they%20began%20assembling%20a%20team%20of%20local%20reporters%20and%20workers%2C%20all%20united%20by%20a%20shared%20vision%20to%20create%20meaningful%20change%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20already%20doing%20our%20part%2C%20performing%20skits%20and%20dramas%20on%20social%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rakesh.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20we%20started%20working%20with%20Nitesh%20Bhai%2C%20we%20realised%20how%20many%20things%20were%20happening%20unsystematically%20in%20our%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20one%20example%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20in%20our%20village%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311641%2Fdigital-activist-upendra-mahanand-uses-twitter-to-address-pension-ration-card-grievances-in-odisha-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20their%20ration%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20often%20charged%20a%20fee.%20We%20later%20found%20out%20that%20getting%20a%20ration%20card%20should%20be%20free.%20The%20person%20in%20charge%20was%20tricking%20them%20into%20paying%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20as%20they%20were%20establishing%20their%20presence%2C%20a%20video%20by%20Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20on%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20garnered%20significant%20attention.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20village%20was%20involved%20in%20making%20that%20film.%20Somehow%2C%20it%20reached%20the%20Collector%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20and%20he%20invited%20us%2C%20asking%20if%20he%20could%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rakesh%20Pawara%20recording%20a%20video%20on%20his%20phone%20which%20will%20be%20shared%20and%20screened%20for%20the%20tribal%20community%20to%20see.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%